&lt;p&gt;Marlowe Park Medical Centre, Kings Family Practice and St Werburgh is an NHS practice in Rochester, Chatham - Kent; we provide primary care to over 20,000 patients from 3 sites.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are in the process of evaluating the way in which we provide care to our patients. Our business plan includes developing a service that will fit the needs of our patients that are in line with the NHS 5 year forward view.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic (Advanced) Nurse Practitioners to work with us. Our ideal candidate for this role will be experienced either in primary care and will be confident with first contact consultations and working at an advanced level of clinical practice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicants will be qualified and experienced in working as independent prescribers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full time post of 37.5 hours over 4 / 5 days a week. We are offering a negotiable salary within the Band 8a and 8b depending on qualifications and experience.&lt;/p&gt;
